Modification of G-Code generator for grill drilling from
http://wiki.linuxcnc.org/cgi-bin/wiki.pl?Simple_LinuxCNC_G-Code_Generators#Grill_Drilling_Software

Additional features:
- don't shift every second line of holes by 1/2 step (selectable)
- optimize tool moving (one line from down to up, next line from up to down).

